data.description: Come and Enjoy the Cool Weather of Payson Az. Completely Updated 2 bedroom 2 bath Condo.Newer appliances , Updated Kitchen cabinets boast black appliance, built in microwave, inset sink and quartz countertops., Solid core doors and updated flooring throughout . Vaulted ceiling  in dining area with picture windows to enjoy pines open to living room with stone surround wood Fireplace. Master with remodeled bath, private exit to patio and walk in closet.Condo Amenities include - Heated Pool, Putting Green, Pickleball / Tennis Court, and BBQ's.
